    • getNumTownBlocks

      public int getNumTownBlocks(TownBlockType townBlockType, TownBlockTypeCache.CacheType cacheType)
      The main getter for a Town's TownBlockTypeCache. Use this to quickly get the number of TownBlocks of a given TownBlockType. Possible CacheTypes: ALL, FORSALE, RESIDENTOWNED
      Parameters:
      townBlockType - TownBlockType which we want to get a count of.
      cacheType - CacheType to filter by.
      Returns:
      number of TownBlocks which have the TownBlockType and meet the CacheType requirement.
